// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2141 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4e578723-875d-594d-ab26-c1f3a512aea7

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
